<tr>
<td><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Jordan" title="Jordan"><img alt="Flag of Jordan" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c0/Flag_of_Jordan.svg/22px-Flag_of_Jordan.svg.png" width="22" height="11" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a></span></td>
